<h2 id="learning-goals">Learning Goals</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Students are familiar with the concepts of virtualization and containerization</li>
  <li>Students are able to interact with a virtualized operating system</li>
  <li>Students are able to deploy an application in a virtualized operating system</li>
</ul>

